name: Pumpkin Cat
description: Pumpkin Cat is a meme token built on the Core Chain blockchain, designed to leverage the popularity of memes and cats within the cryptocurrency community. Purpose and Function: Pumpkin Cat is a meme token that combines the popular elements of memes and cats. It aims to bring a fresh and fun twist to the cryptocurrency space. The token is designed to have growth potential and provide future joy to its holders through its unique and adorable branding. Utility: Pumpkin Cat is a deflationary token with a 0% tax on transactions, making it easy to buy and sell. The project has a total supply of 100,000,000,000,000 PUMP tokens. Liquidity is burned, which is intended to increase the token's scarcity over time.
